These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, thai, mexican, russian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, old-henry, bongani, oliveros
1. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the mexican##1
2. the canadian is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the russian is in an odd position##4
4. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
5. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Nationality   | canadian | thai | russian | mexican |
| Cigar        | aristoff | old-henry   | oliveros | bongani    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, balloon-flower, aconite, orchid
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, brown, yellow, turquise
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
3. the person who likes yellow is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes lilac is the person who growsbellflower##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
6. the person who likes lilac is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Flower   | aconite | bellflower  | balloon-flower  | orchid |
| Color   | turquise    | lilac | yellow | brown    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, tram, bike, skateboard
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, craftsman, tower
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the tower house##3
2. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
3. the tower house is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
4. the tower house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
5. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
6. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Transport          | skateboard | bike | tram    | scooter      |
| House   | craftsman        | tower     | gothic-revival | townhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
House: futuristic, wooden, craftsman, ranch-style
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, alhambra, bongani, davidoff
1. the wooden house is between the havana-smoker and the davidoff-smoker##2
2. the ranch-style house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
3. the bongani-smoker is in an odd position##4
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| House         | ranch-style | futuristic | wooden | craftsman |
| Cigar   | bongani       | havana   | alhambra    | davidoff  |

