.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, february, august, april
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower, lily, orchid
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growssunflower is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growsaconite is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | february  | march    | august   | april       |
| Flower   | aconite | orchid | lily | sunflower |

