.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, zucchini, cabbage, carrot
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, daisy, begonia
1. the person who growsaconite is in an even position##4
2. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food   | cabbage      | zucchini | carrot | cauliflower |
| Flower   | begonia | aconite     | sunflower  | daisy  |

