.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, dunhill, bluemaster, aristoff
4 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, poker, monopoly
1. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
3. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the person playing monopoly is the vegafina-smoker##1
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
6. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | vegafina | aristoff | bluemaster | dunhill    |
| Game     | monopoly | poker  | billiard     | backgammon |

