.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, june, may
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, action
1. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in july##2
6. the person watching disaster movies is in an odd position##4
7. the person watching disaster movies is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person watching musical movies##2
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Birthday   | july | december      | may | june |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | action | disaster    | musical            |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, librarian, journalist, designer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, lacrosse, swimming, volleyball
1. the journalist is on the left or right of the scientist##3
2. the scientist is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the journalist##2
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
5. the journalist is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Job   | designer | librarian   | scientist | journalist |
| Sport    | volleyball     | lacrosse | skateboarding     | swimming  |

