.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
City: hamburg, venice, liverpool, london
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, old-henry, havana, chaman
1. the person traveling to hamburg is the chaman-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the chaman-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person traveling to liverpool##2
4. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
5. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the bluemaster-smoker##3
6. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| City      | venice       | liverpool   | hamburg | london |
| Cigar   | havana | old-henry | chaman        | bluemaster    |

