.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, mechanic, journalist, freelancer
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, chestnut, green, freelancer-polo
1. the person who likes orange is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes green is on the right of the project-manager##1
3. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes freelancer-polo##1
4. the person who likes freelancer-polo is on the left of the journalist##1
5. the mechanic is on the left or right of the journalist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Job   | project-manager   | freelancer   | mechanic      | journalist      |
| Color      | chestnut | green | freelancer-polo | orange |

