.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, colaade, coffee, cola
4 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, pony, horse
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking colaade is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking coffee is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the pony##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | cola | colaade  | coffee  | juice |
| Pet   | horse  | pony | cat | mouse   |

