.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, chaman, siglo, oliveros
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, country, dubstep, funk
1. the fan of country is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the fan of country is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
4. the chaman-smoker is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
6. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Cigar   | chaman | montecristo | siglo | oliveros  |
| Music-Genre     | country   | hip-hop  | funk  | dubstep |

