.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, chinese, spanish, indonesian
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender, blue, amber
1. the person who likes blue is in an odd position##4
2. the polish is in an odd position##4
3. the indonesian is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
5. the polish is on the left or right of the chinese##3
6. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Nationality   | spanish | indonesian | polish | chinese |
| Color           | amber     | apricot     | blue   | lavender         |

