.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lemon, papaya, lime
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, sunflower, poppy
1. the person eating eggplant is between the person who growsbellflower and the person eating lemon##2
2. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person eating lime is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
5. the person who growspoppy is in an odd position##4
6. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Food   | lime | lemon         | eggplant   | papaya |
| Flower   | sunflower    | zinnia | poppy | bellflower   |

