.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
4 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, frog, cat
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, blue, turquise, blood-red
1. the person who likes blood-red is the owner of the frog##1
2. the person who likes turquise is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the person who likes blue is the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
5. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Pet   | bird | lizard | frog    | cat |
| Color   | light-blue   | turquise  | blood-red | blue     |

