.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, may, august, december
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, grapefruit, banana, cauliflower
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4
3. the person eating grapefruit is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
5. the person eating grapefruit is between the person eating cauliflower and the person eating banana##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Birthday         | december   | august | september | may    |
| Food   | banana | grapefruit  | cauliflower     | asparagus |

