.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, may, june, december
City: boston, hamburg, miami, venice
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
7. the person traveling to boston is the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Birthday   | december | august    | june       | may |
| City       | hamburg  | miami | venice | boston  |

