.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, 7up, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur, electrician, mechanic
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the electrician is on the left or right of the accountant##3
3. the accountant is on the left of the electrician##1
4. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the electrician##1
6. the accountant is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | juice | 7up | cola  | milk |
| Job     | accountant      | electrician       | entrepreneur | mechanic     |

