.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, june, january, november
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, western, thriller
1. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
3. the person watching satire movies is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person watching mystery movies##2
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Birthday         | march | january   | november | june |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller          | satire | mystery         | western  |

 